=== 48857771 ulrikrasmussen ===
It writes code as if the audience is you, the user of Claude, and not
other developers reading the code in the future. I found that it helped
to instruct it to keep in mind who the audience is and only write
comments that describe the current state of the code and never describe
anything that can just be inferred from the git history. I found that
that helped, and I almost never see these nonsense comments anymore.
