=== 48850835 vamsiraju ===
I think this is the phase shift 5.6 (Sol set to Ultra) is bringing to
the table. Until now we have become accustomed to asking models to
continue and their natural inclination is always to stop. Now OpenAI
have flipped it around and for the first time are asking us to steer or
stop the model instead, and its own inclination is to keep going. We now
have to decide when we need to steer or want to catch up on our
understanding of the work done but it will keep going.
